&lt;p&gt;
The RB shock absorber has a specially designed  orifice that compensates for varying speeds and loads to consistently decelerate loads without  requiring additional adjustment.  The double  seal enclosure consists of a scraper and a rod seal, provides extra insurance against leakage. The RB series shock absorbers are available in six sizes and all withstand an impact speed of 16 ft/sec.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
The RBQ shock absorber has a double seal enclosure  that consists of a scraper and a rod seal, provides  extra insurance against leakage.  RBQ has a compact design and an interchangeable damper as an option. The RBQ series shock absorbers are available in five sizes and all withstand an impact speed of 3 m/sec.
&lt;/p&gt;
